<D>__{... that somebody would get rich. and, i suppose, the nation would be pretty pissed off.}
<C>__{castor}
<D>__{pissed off, vulnerable... looking for someone to step in, take charge, give them hope again. what if that someone was an f.b.i. hero? a true boy scout and family man with a spotless past. imagine where that guy could land if the timing's right.}
